    <item>
      <title>[입에 착착 붙는 일본어] 적당한 시기를 (가늠) 보다</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/nie/japanese/2024/07/22/66N67EE2GVGZ5N4LVPGFH35H74/</link>
